Class Summary
Class Description
Client
A mirror of the "client" table from the "schooldb" database.
ClientBLL
Based on the request of the controller, it manages the raw input given, validates it, transforms it into essential client data and then applies one of the CRUD operations
ClientDAO
The client data access object are defined here This class extends the genericDAO class.
ClientGUI
The view of the clients management part
ClientGUIController
Controls all the buttons presented in the ClientGUI It calls upon an clientBLL to come and handle the requests made by the user
ClientValidator
